{"tid":299293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯將續約巴塞 成全球最高薪球員","createTime":"2017-06-27T03:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T11:45:18.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8fabeb0659d2963c67ab20599b04d0d6e4597a","tid":299293,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"本身與巴塞合約在2018年屆滿的美斯，正在家鄉準備周末的婚禮，但他與巴塞就續約的談判已達成協議，新約將延至2021年，並在之後可決定再延長多1年。<br />\n<br />\n新約將令美斯獲得除稅後超過2200萬歐元年薪，成為全球最高薪球員。雖然美斯與巴塞已達成協議，但球隊為了可將這筆續約支出撥到新一季財政年度，將待美斯在7月歸隊後才正式動筆簽約。<br />\n<br />\n2200萬歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4946dcfe160be72fe7cfe678749824a95698d9e","tid":299293,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"張約咁似當年月巴果張，又係長約頂薪簽到生涯晚年"},{"pid":"f28408c23b535a8a20449bc1f29e2688df59ffe1","tid":299293,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d2de2f8de506d2370727a967421b15cc19d037","tid":299293,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"唔撚怪得<br />\n<br />\nc朗又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經鋪定路佩雷斯發支持宣言同加薪比佢"},{"pid":"05579d9bd8b0669ae298c4140e556e5333414a80","tid":299293,"uid":99911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚怪得<br />\n<br />\nc朗又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經鋪定路佩雷斯發支持宣言同加薪比佢</blockquote><br />\nC朗眼紅紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d5d5019352a1caee15b597f5411718945f1e3d","tid":299293,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c